# Applies ONLY to `docker build -f Dockerfile.sandbox` (BuildKit per-Dockerfile
# ignore), so it does not affect Dockerfile.api / webapp / landing builds.
# The runner build only needs the .NET sources under src/, so exclude everything
# heavy and irrelevant to keep the build context small.
**/node_modules
**/bin
**/obj
**/dist
**/.vite
.git
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
tests
mkwt
samples
landing
website
docs
docs-internal
k8s
migrations
build
prompts
schemas
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.heic
